    "body": "What you should do is the following:\r\n\r\n\r\n1. Add “attributesToSnippet” to a configure widget\r\n\r\n\r\nThe syntax is the same as using snippeting via settings, it’s an array of attributes. \r\n\r\n2. Use `_snippetResult`\r\n\r\nThis has the same shape as the highlighting. \r\n\r\nHope that helps, feel free to continue commenting here if anything else is unclear. \r\n\r\nHave a nice day!",
